apppot (0.26-1) squeeze; urgency=low

  * Disable consoles in /etc/inittab on install; re-enable them upon remove.
  * Replace /etc/rc.local if it contains `apppot-init.sh` code.
  * Fix dependencies of the `apppot` package.

